ur decor. It\'s also effective at purifying indoor air.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'dracaena',1,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:16','2025-10-11 20:25:10'),(8,1,1,'S-Shaped Bonsai ','A minimalist plant with twisted branches and small leaves, ideal for creating a serene, artistic atmosphere. Perfect for meditation spaces or a Zen aesthetic.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'s-shaped-bonsai',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:16',NULL),(9,1,1,'Peace Lily ','Known for its graceful white flowers, this plant improves air quality and requires little effort to thrive. It\'s an excellent option for beginners.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'peace-lily ',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:16',NULL),(10,1,1,'ZZ Plant (Zamia) ','A near-indestructible plant with glossy, waxy leaves that thrives in neglectful environments. Its modern aesthetic makes it perfect for any space.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'zz-plant',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:17',NULL),(11,1,1,'Snake Plant ','Known for its upright, sword-like leaves, this hardy plant filters toxins and is one of the easiest to care for.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'snake-plant ',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:17',NULL),(12,1,1,'Rubber Plant ','Boasts large, glossy leaves that enhance any interior space. It’s easy to care for and a great option for adding a modern, chic vibe.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'rubber-plant',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:17',NULL),(13,1,1,'Ficus Benjamina ','Commonly known as the Weeping Fig, this plant boasts an elegant appearance with its slender branches and glossy, delicate leaves. It brings a sense of refinement to any space, improving air quality while enhancing decor.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'ficus-benjamina ',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:18',NULL),(14,1,1,'Ficus Panda','A compact and dense variety of ficus, the Ficus Panda features rich, dark green leaves that provide a touch of elegance. Its tidy growth habit makes it a favorite for formal spaces.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'ficus-panda',0,0,0,0,'2024-12-05 21:27:18',NULL),(15,1,1,'Dieffenbachia','Also called Dumb Cane, Dieffenbachia displays bold, variegated leaves in shades of gre